# Joe Decuir

Joseph C. Decuir is an American fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) and a lecturer at the University of Washington's Bothell Campus. Joe was nominated in 2015 for contributions to computer graphics and video games, and has an extensive background in computer and energy technologies.
